title: Jordan 1 Retro High Trophy Room Chicago
description: Limited to just 12,000 pairs, the Trophy Room x Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG SP u2018Chicagou2019 draws inspiration from a moment in NBA history dubbed u2018the freezeoutu2019: in 1985, playing in his first ever All-Star Game, MJ was reportedly denied the ball by established stars who wanted to embarrass the brash rookie. Marcus Jordanu2019s sneaker boutique dresses the high-top in an OG-inspired palette, featuring white leather base with a black Swoosh and red leather overlays in a subtle frozen finish. MJu2019s signature is scrawled across the lateral heel, while a dual-branded patch adorns the sockliner. The sneakeru2019s tooling pairs a vintage off-white midsole with an icy translucent rubber outsole.
